SELECT PF.X5FECPRO, PF.X5MSGTY , PF.X5FUNCTCD, PM.G2MOTACC, CONCAT(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(PF.X5PRIACC, 1, 6),'*****'),SUBSTRING(PF.X5PRIACC, 12, 4)), PF.X5PROCCD,
PF.X5TRAAMN, PF.X5TRADCZ, PF.X5ACQREFN, PF.X5TRAID, PF.X5NRORCL, PF.X5SECRCL 
FROM QS36F.AEXA05PF PF
JOIN QS36F.AEXM1240 XM ON PF.X5NRORCL=XM.XENRORCL
JOIN QS36F.IPMG02PF PM ON PF.X5NRORCL= PM.G2NRORCL AND PF.X5SECRCL=PM.G2SECRCL
WHERE PF.X5NRORCL = '$vNroReclamo$' AND PF.X5FECPRO = '$vFecha_Proceso$' LIMIT 1
